Odaily Planet Daily News According to the monitoring of on-chain analyst Yu Jin, the 50x leveraged whale on Hyperliquid closed its position, and made a total profit of $80,000 from dual-platform and dual-line operations. 
2.24 million US dollars was shorted on ETH on GMX, and the position was quickly closed 5 minutes later to make a profit of $170,000; 
2.3 million US dollars was long ETH and short BTC on Hyperliquid, and 2.46 million USDC was just closed and withdrawn, earning $160,000; 
1.5 million US dollars was long ETH on GMX, and 1.24 million US dollars was just closed and withdrawn, with a loss of $250,000.
